## Installation dev
```python
pip install -e ".[dev,async]"
```

## Code format
Code is auto-formatted on commit with Black and isort via pre-commit.
Install the hooks once after cloning:
```bash
pre-commit install
```
To manually run formatters on all files:
```bash
pre-commit run --all-files --show-diff-on-failure
```

## Tests
```bash
python3 -m pytest --cov=pluxee-api --cov-report term-missing
```


## Tox
Run tox will run
- the tests
- flake 8
- mypy
On multiple python version if you have them installed.

Tox will also run with github actions on multiple python version and multiple OS.
```bash
tox
```

### Running tox across all Python versions (optional, recommended with UV)

[uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) can manage Python installations and speed up tox environments.
Install missing Python versions and the tox-uv plugin:
```bash
uv python install 3.8 3.9 3.10 3.11 3.12 3.13 3.14
pip install tox-uv
```
Then run `tox` as usual — it will use UV to resolve Python interpreters automatically.

## Doc
